              "id": "neg-prompt",
              "name": "promptText",
              "value": "={{ 'TASK: Write an empathetic, professional reply DRAFT for a ' + ($json.starRatingNum <= 2 ? 'negative' : 'neutral') + ' Google review for ' + $json.businessName + '.\\n\\nRULES:\\n- 3 to 5 sentences\\n- Acknowledge the reviewer\\'s experience sincerely — do not be defensive\\n- Apologise where it is appropriate\\n- Invite the reviewer to contact the business directly to resolve the issue\\n- Do NOT include a phone number, email address, or URL — the owner will add contact details before posting\\n- Write in first-person plural (we / our)\\n- Professional, calm, and genuinely empathetic tone\\n- This is a DRAFT for the owner to review — it will not be auto-posted\\n\\nREVIEW DETAILS:\\nBusiness: ' + $json.businessName + '\\nReviewer: ' + $json.reviewerName + '\\nRating: ' + $json.starRatingNum + ' stars\\nReview text: ' + $json.reviewText + '\\n\\nWrite the draft reply now. Reply text only — no labels, no quotation marks.' }}",
